{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778377782093,"sessionID":"ses_1f06cb0b6ffeBBdoPqi94vVlLx","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_TU59mzdkeuCtMRAm2dNJizpn","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can:\\n\\n* **GO term ID and Label**\\n\\n\\nGO:0003400 | regulation of COPII vesicle coating\\n\\n* **Reason for deprecation** Put an x in the appropriate box: \\n\\n - [x] The reason for obsoletion is that the data from the paper for which the term was requested can be accurately described using [appropriate GO term].\\n\\n\\n* **\\\"Replace by\\\" term (ID and label)**\\nIf all annotations can safely be moved to that term\\n\\nCOPII vesicle coating (GO:0048208)\\n\\n\\n* **Are there annotations to this term?**\\n- How many EXP: 11\\n\\nNOTE THAT ONE ANNOTATION (human MAPK15) is incorrect.  I'll dispute this one.\\n\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\\nThe proteins annotated to  GO:0003400 | regulation of COPII vesicle coating\\nare PART_OF the pathway of vesicle coating   (this isn't upstream signalling)\\n\\nAlso, we could rename \\nGO:0048208  COPII vesicle coating\\nto \\\"COPII vesicle coat assembly\\\" (clearer)\\n\\nand \\\"vesicle coating\\\" to  \\\"vesicle coat assembly\\\"\\n\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAw7Wmw\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Dear all, \\n\\nThe proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0003400 regulation of COPII vesicle coating.\\n\\n* The reason for obsoletion is that the data from the paper for which the term was requested can be accurately described using GO:0048208 COPII vesicle coating.\\n\